{"id": 1727, "genre": 1000, "title": "互联网上应该少一些粗暴，你觉得哪些说法可以再审视？", "description": "还有哪些互联网不友好，请勇敢地在留言区揭露。( 题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 9237, "comment_count": 56, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170614083850HTLx8VwAc9BCrmIG.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-13T17:00:20Z", "questions": [{"id": 2412, "title": "互联网上应该少一些粗暴，你觉得哪些说法可以再审视？", "content": "互联网上应该少一些粗暴，除了性取向，你觉得还有什么可以再审视？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 210113, "content": "从广告到舆论，总说我不懂/应该/值得去做某些事，但我并不介意啊", "image": "img/option/option/20170606133744vXktsPoNIME3zKeF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210114, "content": "明明是中性的，却被劝慰，比如一定要把“内向”和不懂交际联系起来吗", "image": "img/option/option/20170606133813bSTAsjzgDVFq0JBW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210115, "content": "对时事发表了几句见解就被质疑“你要当公知吗”", "image": "img/option/option/20170606134048wJeQECvsT2O4xGFZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210116, "content": "女权主义者也尊重男性的平等权利，“女权”只是个表述而已", "image": "img/option/option/20170606134133xymTKkOC5Nh2eDP7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210117, "content": "喜欢明星被称为脑残粉，讨厌明星就被叫做无脑黑，不喜不厌就是没态度", "image": "img/option/option/20170606134217gryAeW6HGvtsmMwF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210121, "content": "表现得温和善意，就被称为圣母，一提出反对就被叫喷子", "image": "img/option/option/20170606143814fVH5Lg2mdonatZKC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210122, "content": "任何问题都能归结到“这是个看脸的社会”", "image": "img/option/option/20170606144131xXSZadILN5nBlKsw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210128, "content": "称赞任何东西，也会被指责不客观，“XX就不好吗”", "image": "img/option/option/2017060614564856obCMFtWseIQ9iq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}